43 (d) The tax commissioner, chief clerk, executive secretary, and administrative specialist
44 shall be entitled to any other compensation or salary increase as provided for by law as well
45 as any cost-of-living increase or merit increase provided to county employees by the
46 governing authority of Cobb County."
47 SECTION 2.
48 All laws and parts of laws in conflict with this Act are repealed.
